Non nurturing trainers despite having already feedback to the trainer. My kid has been enjoying gymnastic at another gym that has shifted. My kid has only been to two sessions but now refuse to attend further sessions, citing that trainers will tell her that they rather she leave the academy than teach her.

A nice place for kids to start learning gymnastics with nurturing coaches. Love that the coaches encourages the kids to perform their best and works with them individually to work on specific areas for improvement.
The coach is very patient with students and conducts class in a calm and safe manner. He makes class enjoyable while ensuring it‚Äôs suitable and safe for different age groups.

The  Gymnastic is having good infrastructure and coaches are very friendly. The suggestion is they should be more kids friendly in terms of allowing the parents to be with smaller kids occasionally to make them comfortable with the coaches.
